          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "And, for the grand finale, we stopped by the River Nethy. The name Abernethy translates to \"by the River Nethy\", so this was a mandatory stop. Much to Daniel's dismay, the Rivery Nethy was not the mighty body of water he had dreamed of. In fact, it was just a tiny little stream. I thought it was cute though. :)"
          }
